The '''Dawn Rumble''' or '''Little Dawn Rumble''' was a [[Killik/Legends|Killik]] [[Reproduction/Legends|mating]] dance. After it was performed, Killiks would go to the [[Harem Cave]] to mate, and [[Joiner]]s would go off as well, presumably for the same purpose. [[Jaina Solo Fel|Jaina Solo]] fantasized about [[Jagged Fel]] becoming a Joiner, as it would make the Dawn Rumble "more interesting."

